<td>01/05/1987</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr><tr><td>Telephone allowance</td>
<td>01/07/2004</td>
<td>Other than that paid to the holder of a <a href="../guide-social-security-law/acronyms#cshc" title="Commonwealth seniors health card">CSHC</a>.</td>
